title: BATMAN - LI'L GOTHAM 023 (2013) (digital) (Son of Ultron-Empire)
description:
PENULTIMATE ISSUE! Final issue - #24 - will be out next month.

(Jesus Christ, DC Comics. Cancel all the good comics much? Do you people just WANT your digital comics to fail?)  --STF

------

Damian's fowlest friend Jerry has disappeared, but the people of Gotham are not cooperative in his search for a missing turkey. But there are November holidays that aren't Thanksgiving, and the Condiment King is making a Sandwich Day run!
